        {
            "title": "歐盟接近就俄羅斯資產凍結事宜達成協議 有望疏通援烏癥結點",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 歐盟勢將於周五批准一項協議，動用緊急權力延長對俄羅斯資產的凍結 —— 這是動用這些資金援助烏克蘭的關鍵一步。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據知情人士透露，歐盟委員會周四提出了該提案，成員國代表已初步批准該提案，為周五達成最終協議鋪平道路。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐盟尋求利用被凍結的俄羅斯央行資產為烏克蘭提供900億歐元（1050億美元）貸款，而上述問題已成為主要癥結所在。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">目前歐盟成員國必須每六個月續期這一資產凍結措施，這引發外界擔憂匈牙利或其他國家可能行使否決權，導致莫斯科突然獲得其資金索取權。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-0884b9d6-6a32-304c-88b0-255d5bee14c3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士透露，歐盟委員會的提案將延長六個月周期，且每次續期僅需獲得合格多數國家支持。此舉實質上將確保高達2100億歐元的俄羅斯資產繼續留在歐盟境內。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士表示，歐盟委員會正尋求將凍結措施的延長期限決定，與利用這筆資金向烏克蘭提供貸款這一更大目標分離開來，因為對該問題的討論尚未達成共識。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士稱，絕大多數成員國支持該策略，但部分國家態度猶豫，匈牙利則強烈反對。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題EU Nears Russian Asset Freeze Deal to Ease Ukraine Loan (2)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Iain Rogers.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">(更新前兩段信息)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%AD%90%E7%9B%9F%E5%B0%8B%E6%B1%82%E6%9C%80%E6%97%A9%E6%96%BC%E5%91%A8%E4%BA%94%E5%B0%B1%E4%BF%84%E7%BE%85%E6%96%AF%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2%E5%87%8D%E7%B5%90%E4%BA%8B%E5%AE%9C%E9%81%94%E6%88%90%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-%E7%96%8F%E9%80%9A%E6%8F%B4%E7%83%8F%E7%99%A5%E7%B5%90%E9%BB%9E-120828355.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-12 02:11:01",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "橡樹資本創始人：聯儲會進一步降息意義不大 反而助長市場冒險",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 橡樹資本管理公司聯合創始人霍華德·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:馬克斯;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/馬克斯\">馬克斯</a>警告稱，隨著回報環境趨於溫和，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:聯儲會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯儲會\">聯儲會</a>圍繞資金成本的「操作」將把人們推向更高風險的投資，他認為利率比當前水平再低很多並無意義。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">馬克斯在接受彭博電視採訪時表示：「我認為，聯儲會在大多數時候應保持被動，只有在經濟嚴重過熱、趨向惡性通膨，或嚴重低迷、無法創造就業時，才應出手相救，但目前並非這種情況。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯儲會周三將利率下調25基點至2022年以來最低水平，不過央行內部對於疲軟勞動力市場和頑固通膨哪個對經濟構成更大威脅存在分歧。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-4490184f-5f5a-39fb-9fec-d967d18fa3ad-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統川普認為聯儲會應該把降息幅度翻倍，但馬克斯認為，過度廉價的資金成本會令市場想當然地認為央行會介入並解決市場問題，從而助長冒險行為。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他說：「在一個中等回報環境中，你如何獲取高回報？大多數人的辦法是承擔更多風險，除非機會特別有吸引力，否則我不喜歡這樣做。」。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"橡樹資本管理公司聯合創始人霍華德·馬克斯表示，利率無需比現在低很多。來源： 彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/YNLrgyWirtf0yhnyMyN1mA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/409515511914e303a1c400ae8533a5ba\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">橡樹資本管理公司聯合創始人霍華德·馬克斯表示，利率無需比現在低很多。來源： 彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Howard Marks Warns of Little Merit in Further Fed Rate Cuts (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Lisa Abramowicz.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%A9%A1%E6%A8%B9%E8%B3%87%E6%9C%AC%E5%89%B5%E5%A7%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E9%80%B2-%E6%AD%A5%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E6%84%8F%E7%BE%A9%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%A7-%E5%8F%8D%E8%80%8C%E5%8A%A9%E9%95%B7%E5%B8%82%E5%A0%B4%E5%86%92%E9%9A%AA-162548854.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-12 02:11:04",
